{{spanish name|Flores|Ferrando}}
'''Ignacio Flores Ferrando''' (born July 31, 1990 in [[Montevideo]]), commonly known as Ignacio Flores, is a [[Uruguay]]an [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[striker]] for [[RCD Mallorca B]].

